findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInReward() and _getCurrentSupply() use loops to find and remove addresses from the _excluded list and evaluate total supply respectively. If there is a long excluded addresses list, these functions may be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to change tax and liquidity fee, maximum transaction amount, exclude from fees, withdraw ERC20 tokens and BNBs, lock and unlock, which can be used to retake privileges even after ownership was renounced.
